{"id":232782144,"title":"〈對不起讓你失望〉","content":"有時候好想放棄\n抓著我的人讓我痛苦\n可不可以放走我\n我害怕這真的成為我\n永遠的歸途\n\n不能向前走就好嗎？\n我不想回頭了\n你怎麼可以微笑著迎接我\n怎麼可以忽略我的影子\n我就快被淹沒了\n\n淹沒很好\n為什麼叫醒我\n為什麼為我鬆綁\n又把囚繩送給我\n\n游泳的時候\n聽得到大海的聲音嗎\n「為什麼不擁抱我？」\n「為什麼不擁抱我？」\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n291219/","excerpt":"有時候好想放棄，抓著我的人讓我痛苦，可不可以放走我，我害怕這真的成為我，永遠的歸途，不能向前走就好嗎？我不想回頭了，你怎麼可以微笑著迎接我，怎麼可以忽略我的影子，我就快被淹沒了，淹沒很好，為什麼叫醒我","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-29T07:22:00.455Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-29T07:22:00.455Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":4,"tags":["HIDE_THUMBNAIL"],"topics":[],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"別","department":"annaxx___","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":4}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[],"postAvatar":""}